&lt;li&gt;Review drawings, specifications, and bid documents to prepare detailed electrical estimates&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform quantity takeoffs and develop labor, material, and subcontractor pricing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Solicit and evaluate vendor and subcontractor quotes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify value engineering opportunities and cost-saving strategies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare and present bid proposals and scope clarifications&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in bid reviews and project handoff meetings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
