&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Summary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking an Electrical Safety Manager to develop, implement, and continuously improve the company’s electrical safety program.&amp;nbsp; This role services as the subject-matter expert for electrical hazards and safe work practices.&amp;nbsp; The Electrical Safety Manager drives proactive safety behaviors, reduces risk, and embeds electrical safety into daily work execution.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
