&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish and lead a safety-first culture where safety is owned by field leadership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as a visible safety leader through regular job site visits and field engagement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop, implement, and maintain comprehensive electrical safety programs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure compliance with OSHA, NFPA 70E, and state and local safety regulations&lt;/li&gt;
