&lt;li&gt;Ability to complete OSHA documentation and reporting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Valid driver’s license with clean driving record&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Willingness to travel regularly to job sites&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Title:&lt;/strong&gt; Journeyman Electrician&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Company:&lt;/strong&gt; Bertke Electric&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location:&lt;/strong&gt; Ghent, KY&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Schedule:&lt;/strong&gt; Day Shift (7:00 AM – 3:30 PM)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Overview:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Bertke Electric is seeking a skilled and dependable Journeyman Electrician to support operations at a steel mill facility in Ghent, KY. This role involves maintaining, troubleshooting, and repairing electrical systems in a heavy industrial environment. The ideal candidate is safety-focused, reliable, and experienced in industrial electrical work.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Install, maintain, and repair electrical systems and equipment in a steel mill environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Troubleshoot and diagnose electrical issues efficiently to minimize downtime&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bend and install rigid conduit and related components&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with a variety of tools, equipment, and lift systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow all safety procedures and company policies in a high-risk industrial setting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with team members and other trades as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Requirements:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Valid and current Journeyman Electrician license in the state of Kentucky (preferred, not required)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven experience working in an industrial environment (steel mill experience preferred)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong troubleshooting and problem-solving skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to read and interpret electrical drawings and schematics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reliable attendance and strong work ethic&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Physical Requirements:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to sit, stand, bend, and move for extended periods&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to lift up to 50 pounds&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to climb stairs and work at heights using lifts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to bend rigid conduit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Compensation &amp;amp; Benefits:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competitive pay (based on experience)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Medical, dental, and vision insurance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;401(k) with company match&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Paid time off (PTO)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Paid holidays&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Equal Opportunity Employer:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bertke Electric Co. is an equal opportunity employer. We value diversity and do not discriminate based on race, color, religion, sex, national origin, age, disability, or any other protected status.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Journeyman Electrician (Commercial Service)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location:&lt;/strong&gt; Greater Cincinnati, OH / Northern Kentucky&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Schedule:&lt;/strong&gt; Day Shift (7:00 AM – 3:30 PM)&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Travel:&lt;/strong&gt; Up to 50% (overnight travel required)&lt;/p&gt;
