&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a skilled and dependable Journeyman Electrician to join our growing team serving the Greater Cincinnati and Northern Kentucky region. This role focuses primarily on commercial service work, including troubleshooting, maintenance, and repair of electrical systems.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an excellent opportunity for a licensed professional looking for steady daytime hours, strong benefits, and the chance to work with a well-supported service team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform commercial electrical service, maintenance, and repair work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Diagnose and troubleshoot electrical issues in commercial environments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Install, maintain, and repair electrical systems and components&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Read and interpret blueprints, schematics, and technical drawings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure all work complies with applicable codes, standards, and safety regulations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate effectively with customers, team members, and management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in an on-call rotation for after-hours service needs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
