&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Active Journeyman Electrician License in Kentucky (required)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum of 4 years of electrical experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to travel up to 50%, including overnight stays&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to meet the physical demands of the trade (lifting, climbing, standing, etc.)&lt;/li&gt;
