&lt;p&gt;We are expanding and seeking a skilled&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;250&quot; data-end=&quot;276&quot;&gt;Low Voltage Technician&lt;/strong&gt; to install, maintain, and troubleshoot a variety of low voltage systems in commercial and industrial environments in the Cincinnati area. This role includes working with security systems, access control, fire alarm systems, data/communication networks, and audiovisual equipment. The ideal candidate is detail-oriented, customer-focused, and comfortable working independently or as part of a team.&lt;/p&gt;
